OL,3,CConservatives have the most to lose in
OL,4,Ctheir traditional southern heartlands
OL,6,FPolling stations have now closed and
OL,7,FConservative supporters face an
OL,8,Fanxious 24 hours to find out their
OL,9,Ffate in the South.
OL,11,FThe Tories have the most to lose in
OL,12,Ftheir traditional southern heartlands,
OL,13,Fwhere they are battling to keep
OL,14,Frunning the flagship county councils
OL,15,Fof Hampshire, East Sussex and West
OL,16,FSussex.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/11
