OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,417,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1778234502
OL,3,CConservatives have the most to lose in
OL,4,Ctheir traditional southern heartlands
OL,6,FThat result stems from 2021, when
OL,7,FBoris Johnson was Tory leader and
OL,8,Fprime minister, and doing well in the
OL,9,Fopinion polls as the coronavirus
OL,10,Fvaccine was rolled out.
OL,12,FA bad night would see the
OL,13,FConservatives lose all three county
OL,14,Fcouncils. A terrible night would see
OL,15,Fthem replaced as the largest party by
OL,16,Fthe Liberal Democrats or Reform UK.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/11
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
