OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,417,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41606
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1778234502
OL,3,CConservatives have the most to lose in
OL,4,Ctheir traditional southern heartlands
OL,6,FReading Borough Council has been
OL,7,FLabour majority controlled since 2012.
OL,8,FThe party is also fighting to keep
OL,9,Fcontrol of councils in Adur, Crawley,
OL,10,FSouthampton, Swindon, Thurrock and
OL,11,FWorthing.
OL,13,FSeveral senior Cabinet ministers have
OL,14,Fmade campaign visits to the council
OL,15,Fareas, in a sign of the degree of
OL,16,Fnervousness in Labour high command.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/11
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
