PN,41607
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1778234502
OL,3,CConservatives have the most to lose in
OL,4,Ctheir traditional southern heartlands
OL,6,FThe Liberal Democrats have been
OL,7,Ftargeting Surrey, where elections are
OL,8,Fbeing held for two new unitary
OL,9,Fauthorities, due to take over the
OL,10,Frunning of all council services in
OL,11,F2027.
OL,13,FSir Ed Davey's party also hopes to
OL,14,Fmake inroads in Hampshire and Sussex,
OL,15,Fwhere they increased their number of
OL,16,FMPs in the 2024 general election.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G7/11
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
