FL,417,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41608
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1778234502
OL,3,CConservatives have the most to lose in
OL,4,Ctheir traditional southern heartlands
OL,6,FReform UK is hoping to win a large
OL,7,Fnumber of seats on Essex County
OL,8,FCouncil, and potentially even repeat
OL,9,Fthe landslide win they secured across
OL,10,Fthe border in Kent last year.
OL,12,FNigel Farage's party has also been
OL,13,Ftargeting Hastings and Worthing, where
OL,14,Fthere are borough elections, and the
OL,15,FIsle of Wight, where all seats are to
OL,16,Fplay for on the island's unitary
OL,17,Fcouncil.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G8/11
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
