OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,417,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41609
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1778234502
OL,3,CConservatives have the most to lose in
OL,4,Ctheir traditional southern heartlands
OL,6,FThe Greens also hope to make gains in
OL,7,FEast Sussex, and may even take
OL,8,Foutright control of Hastings Borough
OL,9,FCouncil, where they currently have a
OL,10,Fminority administration.
OL,12,FThe biggest winner of 2026's local
OL,13,Felections in the South and South East
OL,14,Fmight be 'NOC' ` not a new party, but
OL,15,F'no overall control'.
OL,17,FWhen our first-past-the-post electoral
OL,18,Fsystem collides with five party
OL,19,Fpolitics, it is likely to see lots of
OL,20,Fcouncils where no single party has a
OL,21,Fmajority of council seats.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G9/11
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,417,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41610
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1778234502
OL,3,CConservatives have the most to lose in
OL,4,Ctheir traditional southern heartlands
OL,6,FThat could make it difficult for
OL,7,Fauthorities to set budgets and make
OL,8,Fmajor decisions.
OL,10,FRegardless, many of the new
OL,11,Fcouncillors elected on 7th May will
OL,12,Fonly serve two-year terms of office,
OL,13,Fbefore their councils are abolished.
OL,15,FIt could mean lots of trips to the
OL,16,Fballot box over the coming years for
OL,17,Fvoters, when polls suggest high levels
OL,18,Fof apathy with politics.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}  G10/11
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
